      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "REDDING, Cal, Oct. 30.-The\nrush at the United States land\nOffice to get into line to locate\non 100000 acres of land which will\nbe subject to homestead or timber\nclaims in Shasta, Trinity and Sis\nkiyou counties tomorrow, grows\neach hour. A long line Of locaters\nIs waiting. Last night 60 men and\nwomen slept at their posts. Today\nlocaters are paying as high as $40\nfor men to stand in their places in\nline. Many more locaters are ex-\npected during the day. Trouble is\nanticipated tomorrow."
    }
  ]
